caption.text:
How to Create Crazy Converting Ads ⬇️

I get asked all the time about how to use your organic content for your ads! There are two main ways: 

#1. This guy nailed it, you take your best performing content and make it into an ad, you can adjust the CTA so it still works!

#2. Build up your personal brand, then create ads that target your following. Because they already know you, the chances of conversion are much higher! A great example of this is Alex Hormzi!

Follow for more social media marketing education! ✅
